data.description: A true 4 bedroom home is waiting for a new family!  Lots of windows so the home is very light!  The layout of this home is wonderful and spacious and the backyard is manageable.  There is a formal dining that makes for many gathering opportunities.  A half bath if just off the kitchen with a lot of cabinet space throughout the home.  The primary closet is an Australian closet and so spacious.  Don't miss this opportunity!  Copperfield is  centrally located in Edmond and it is an established neighborhood, sporting a large neighborhood pool and park.  The HOA is $285 per year.
